3a4ee3c58671ccada23/HOPFAB-MATERIAUTHEQUE-071-HD.jpg\" data-link=\"/le-travail-des-teintes-sur-la-lave-emaillee/hopfab-materiautheque-071-hd/\" class=\"wp-image-5823\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/6caa86d1d4e403a4ee3c58671ccada23/HOPFAB-MATERIAUTHEQUE-071-HD.jpg?resize=1024%2C683&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/6caa86d1d4e403a4ee3c58671ccada23/HOPFAB-MATERIAUTHEQUE-071-HD.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/6caa86d1d4e403a4ee3c58671ccada23/HOPFAB-MATERIAUTHEQUE-071-HD.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/6caa86d1d4e403a4ee3c58671ccada23/HOPFAB-MATERIAUTHEQUE-071-HD.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/6caa86d1d4e403a4ee3c58671ccada23/HOPFAB-MATERIAUTHEQUE-071-HD.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/6caa86d1d4e403a4ee3c58671ccada23/HOPFAB-MATERIAUTHEQUE-071-HD.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/6caa86d1d4e403a4ee3c58671ccada23/HOPFAB-MATERIAUTHEQUE-071-HD.jpg?resize=1568%2C1045&amp;ssl=1 1568w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/6caa86d1d4e403a4ee3c58671ccada23/HOPFAB-MATERIAUTHEQUE-071-HD.jpg?w=2250&amp;ssl=1 2250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></figure></li></ul><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption\">Echantillons de la matériauthèque Hopfab</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/le-travail-des-teintes-sur-la-lave-emaillee\\/\"}' style=\"height:60px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"has-very-dark-gray-color has-text-color\">Avantages :</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Elle est reconnue pour sa grande <strong>résistance aux UV</strong>, la tenue des couleurs n’est en effet pas altérée suite à l’exposition aux UV.&nbsp;</li><li>L’émail est très r<strong>ésistant aux conditions climatiques</strong> les plus extrêmes : fortes chaleurs, gel, pluie, grêle, neige… !</li><li>Les émaux étant <strong>miscibles </strong>entre eux, toutes les couleurs sont possibles ou presque ! L’atelier d’Emmanuel préfère d’ailleurs travailler avec des couleurs <strong>sur-mesure.</strong></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/le-travail-des-teintes-sur-la-lave-emaillee\\/\"}' style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-1 is-cropped\"><ul data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/le-travail-des-teintes-sur-la-lave-emaillee\\/\"}' class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img data-attachment-id=\"5826\" data-permalink=\"/le-travail-des-teintes-sur-la-lave-emaillee/materiautheque-149/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?fit=4500%2C3000&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"4500,3000\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Thibault Pousset&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 5D Mark IV&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1568816783&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;\\u00a9Thibault Pousset Photographe&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;39&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;800&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.016666666666667&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"MATERIAUTHEQUE-149\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?fit=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?fit=750%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?resize=750%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"5826\" data-full-url=\"/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg\" data-link=\"/le-travail-des-teintes-sur-la-lave-emaillee/materiautheque-149/\" class=\"wp-image-5826\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?resize=1024%2C683&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?resize=1568%2C1045&amp;ssl=1 1568w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/5e9ac109aa84fad151841aa742723694/MATERIAUTHEQUE-149.jpg?w=2250&amp;ssl=1 2250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Echantillons de la matériauthèque Hopfab</figcaption></figure></li></ul></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#555252;font-size:12.5px\"></p>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/le-travail-des-teintes-sur-la-lave-emaillee\\/\"}' style=\"height:60px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"has-very-dark-gray-color has-text-color\">Limites</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Il est difficile d’obtenir un mélange parfait comme pour une peinture ou une laque.</li><li>Suivant la finition désirée, l’intensité de la couleur ne sera pas la même. Pour une finition brillante la teinte sera très vive, ce qui ne sera pas le cas avec une finition mat ou satinée.</li><li>Certaines couleurs sont difficiles à obtenir voire impossibles telles que des couleurs très vives (rose fushia, vert intense ou jaune vif) ou fluorescentes.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/le-travail-des-teintes-sur-la-lave-emaillee\\/\"}' style=\"height:11px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/le-travail-des-teintes-sur-la-lave-emaillee\\/\"}' class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img data-attachment-id=\"5830\" data-permalink=\"/le-travail-des-teintes-sur-la-lave-emaillee/pi268-1-lave-emaillee-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/1e6fd2faee10580027a41531a9937cc1/PI268-1-Lave-emaillee-2.jpg?fit=4410%2C2940&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"4410,2940\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;16&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Thibault Pousset&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 5D Mark IV&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1571326272&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;\\u00a9Thibault Pousset Photographe&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.008&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"PI268-1-Lave-emaillee-2\" data-image-d